README : xosd_message 0.1
GPL by Bernd Mueller < ragnar76@googlemail.com >
22.01.2007

xosd_message is a small tool to display messages on your X11 screen. just
start it with >> xosd_message "Message you want to display" <<. If you want
to diplay more than a single word, just put the phrase in quotes as you see
above. Thats it.  